{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":777,"text":"Today, I'm going to talk to you about sketching electronics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5193,"text":"I'm, among several other things, an electrical engineer,"},{"time":10561,"text":"and that means that I spend a good amount of time"},{"time":14258,"text":"designing and building new pieces of technology,"},{"time":18632,"text":"and more specifically designing and building electronics."},{"time":23172,"text":"And what I've found is that the process of designing"},{"time":27530,"text":"and building electronics is problematic in all sorts of ways."},{"time":33124,"text":"So it's a really slow process, it's really expensive,"},{"time":37965,"text":"and the outcome of that process,"},{"time":40405,"text":"namely electronic circuit boards,"},{"time":42821,"text":"are limited in all sorts of kind of interesting ways."},{"time":45850,"text":"So they're really small, generally, they're square"},{"time":49490,"text":"and flat and hard, and frankly, most of them"},{"time":53855,"text":"just aren't very attractive, and so my team and I"},{"time":58168,"text":"have been thinking of ways to really change and mix up"},{"time":62156,"text":"the process and the outcome of designing electronics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66817,"text":"And so what if you could design and build electronics"},{"time":70905,"text":"like this? So what if you could do it extremely quickly,"},{"time":74945,"text":"extremely inexpensively, and maybe more interestingly,"},{"time":80610,"text":"really fluidly and expressively and even improvisationally?"},{"time":85874,"text":"Wouldn't that be so cool, and that wouldn't that open up"},{"time":89196,"text":"all sorts of new possibilities?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91644,"text":"I'm going to share with you two projects that are"},{"time":95028,"text":"investigations along these lines, and we'll start with this one."},{"time":99737,"text":"(Video) Magnetic electronic pieces and ferrous paper."},{"time":105474,"text":"A conductive pen from the Lewis lab at UIUC."},{"time":109306,"text":"Sticker templates."},{"time":112180,"text":"Speed x 4."},{"time":130259,"text":"Making a switch."},{"time":142209,"text":"Music: DJ Shadow."},{"time":160175,"text":"Adding some intelligence with a microcontroller."},{"time":176735,"text":"Sketching an interface."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184268,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":193635,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":197805,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203511,"text":"Pretty cool, huh? We think so."},{"time":206508,"text":"So now that we developed these tools"},{"time":210292,"text":"and found these materials that let us do these things,"},{"time":214030,"text":"we started to realize that, essentially, anything"},{"time":218198,"text":"that we can do with paper, anything that we can do"},{"time":220582,"text":"with a piece of paper and a pen"},{"time":222997,"text":"we can now do with electronics."},{"time":225414,"text":"So the next project that I want to show you is kind of a"},{"time":227782,"text":"deeper exploration of that possibility."},{"time":231342,"text":"And I'll kind of let it speak for itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235206,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":325652,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331020,"text":"So the next step for us in this process"},{"time":335820,"text":"is now to find a way to let all of you"},{"time":339548,"text":"build things like this,"},{"time":342444,"text":"and so the way that we're approaching that is by"},{"time":345524,"text":"teaching workshops to people where we explain"},{"time":348131,"text":"how they can use these kinds of tools, and then also"},{"time":351244,"text":"working to get the tools and the materials and techniques"},{"time":354986,"text":"out into the real world in a variety of ways."},{"time":358736,"text":"And so sometime soon, you'll be able to play and build"},{"time":362320,"text":"and sketch with electronics in this fundamentally new way."},{"time":366114,"text":"So thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}